room_title: Escape room "Cabin In The Woods" by Nut House Escape Rooms in Rochester (NY)
review: Super fun!! Challenging, but doable. Loved the effects! Fun thing to do with a group of friends or family members over the holidays.

room_title: Escape room "Cabin In The Woods" by Nut House Escape Rooms in Rochester (NY)
review: Had a great time! 10/10 would recommend! The room was challenging and the storyline was engaging. I liked that they didn't give you too much information, and the use of special effects made the experience very real.
